Sentencas: An approach was developed towards design of medium-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells based on a deformation strengthened Ni-Al alloy.
Titulo: Design of Medium-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Porous Supports of Deformation Strengthened Ni-Al Alloy

Sentencas: Methods of sintering were described that allowed obtaining layers of complex oxides with ionic and mixed conductivity and with regulated porosity in the range of 40-1%.
Titulo: Design of Medium-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Porous Supports of Deformation Strengthened Ni-Al Alloy

Sentencas: Power density of a fuel cell on a metallic support reaches 500 mW/cm(2) already at 700 degrees C when humid H-2 was used as fuel and air was used as an oxidant.
Titulo: Design of Medium-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Porous Supports of Deformation Strengthened Ni-Al Alloy

Sentencas: Analysis of fuel cell cross-section after tests showed absence of fractures, flaking, and new phases with low conductivity, which proves good compatibility of all materials used in fuel cell design.
Titulo: Design of Medium-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells on Porous Supports of Deformation Strengthened Ni-Al Alloy
